{"type":"message","id":"70fa7538","parentId":"e7a5e7d7","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:30:06.517Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let's work through this step by step. First, I need to follow the instructions from AGENTS.md for the session startup sequence. Let's check which files to read.\n\nFrom AGENTS.md:\n1. Read SOUL.md\n2. Read USER.md\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday)\n4. If in MAIN SESSION, also read MEMORY.md\n\nFirst, let's check today's date. Since the current time zone is Asia/Hong_Kong, let's get today's date. Wait, maybe I should check if the memory directory exists and what files are there. Let's list the workspace first.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Let's start by exploring the workspace and reading the required files for session startup."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_eizgug4x6tpa6wtl1te2a8zi","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\" -Force","workdir":"D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":4700,"output":368,"cacheRead":8248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13316,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772591397557}}
