{"type":"message","id":"3b2da606","parentId":"2ed19de0","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:44:27.180Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ndvesuztd5lfxvfsb4m3n6g0","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Stop-Service : �������´����޷�ֹͣ����Tailscale (Tailscale)��: �޷��򿪼������.���ϵ� Tailscale ����\r\n����λ�� ��:1 �ַ�: 1\r\n+ Stop-Service -Name Tailscale -Force; Start-Sleep -Seconds 2; Remove-I ...\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : CloseError: (System.ServiceProcess.ServiceController:ServiceController) [Stop-Service]��S\r\n    erviceCommandException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : CouldNotStopService,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.StopServiceCommand"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":4391,"aggregated":"Stop-Service : �������´����޷�ֹͣ����Tailscale (Tailscale)��: �޷��򿪼������.���ϵ� Tailscale ����\r\n����λ�� ��:1 �ַ�: 1\r\n+ Stop-Service -Name Tailscale -Force; Start-Sleep -Seconds 2; Remove-I ...\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : CloseError: (System.ServiceProcess.ServiceController:ServiceController) [Stop-Service]��S\r\n    erviceCommandException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : CouldNotStopService,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.StopServiceCommand","cwd":"D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772592267178}}
{"type":"message","id":"773e68a6","parentId":"3b2da606","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:44:46.237Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, so we can't stop the service because we need administrator privileges. Let's summarize the possible solutions for 李工, since we've tried a few things. The main issues could be:\n\n1. Need to run Tailscale as administrator\n2. Default browser issue\n3. Network/proxy issue\n4. Corrupted Tailscale state, which requires resetting (needs admin)\n\nLet's list the steps for 李工 to try, since some of them need admin privileges.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我帮你排查了一圈，针对 Tailscale 点击 \"sign in\" 完全没反应的问题，给你几个解决方案（有些需要管理员权限）：\n\n## 解决方案\n\n### 方案 1：以管理员身份运行 Tailscale（最推荐）\n1. 右键点击系统托盘中的 Tailscale 图标 → 退出\n2. 打开开始菜单，找到 Tailscale\n3. 右键点击 Tailscale → 选择\"以管理员身份运行\"\n4. 再尝试点击 \"sign in\"\n\n### 方案 2：重置 Tailscale 状态（需要管理员）\n1. 以管理员身份打开 PowerShell\n2. 依次运行以下命令：\n   ```powershell\n   Stop-Service -Name Tailscale -Force\n   Remove-Item -Path \"$env:LOCALAPPDATA\\Tailscale\\*\" -Recurse -Force\n   Remove-Item -Path \"C:\\ProgramData\\Tailscale\\*\" -Recurse -Force\n   Start-Service -Name Tailscale\n   ```\n3. 重新打开 Tailscale，再尝试 sign in\n\n### 方案 3：检查网络环境\n- 确保网络可以访问 `https://login.tailscale.com`\n- 如果使用了代理或 VPN，暂时关闭后再试\n- 检查 Windows Defender 防火墙是否阻止了 Tailscale\n\n### 方案 4：完全卸载后重装\n1. 打开设置 → 应用 → 已安装的应用\n2. 找到 Tailscale，点击卸载\n3. 重启电脑\n4. 重新下载官网安装包：https://tailscale.com/download/windows\n5. **重要**：安装时右键点击安装包 → \"以管理员身份运行\"\n\n你想先尝试哪个方案？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":489,"output":583,"cacheRead":47160,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48232,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772592267181}}
